      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>BLUE NOTE</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>So it seems that god himself</l>
          <l>had taught you how to play the guitar.</l>
          <l>He gave you the tone, the song, the rhythm</l>
          <l>So you'll be a star</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>I adore creating music too</l>
          <l>The way I'm playing it with you</l>
          <l>And I know</l>
          <l>Improvization is happiness</l>
          <l>Yes, It's solitude</l>
          <l>I confess</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>playing through those last few verses</l>
          <l>Your last round in closing phase</l>
          <l>The entire city lost their senses</l>
          <l>You're the song, the sky, the jazz</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>Fly with your song all over the city</l>
          <l>Sing for the people</l>
          <l>It is sunset the poem's ending</l>
          <l>Open your eyes, it's time for landing</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
